---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Safe Docx - AI-Native Word Document Editing
description: Deterministic DOCX operations for AI systems. Fast, safe, composable edits that preserve document integrity.
---
{# ── Hero ────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Safe DOCX</p>
  <h1>Deterministic DOCX editing with auditable behavior.</h1>
  <p>
    Safe DOCX keeps edits local-first and spec-driven — 22 tools for reading, writing, commenting, formatting, and tracking changes in Word documents. No remote servers, no black boxes.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-copy">
    <code class="install-copy">npx -y @usejunior/safe-docx</code>
    <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="npx -y @usejunior/safe-docx" aria-label="Copy npx command">
      <span class="copy-label">Copy</span>
    </button>
  </div>
  <p class="install-hint">Run in your terminal to start the MCP server</p>

  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="cta" href="#install">Install Guide</a>
    <a class="cta cta-ghost" href="trust/index.html">Trust Evidence</a>
  </div>

  <div class="badge-stack">
    <div class="badge-row">
      <a class="trust-badge" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@usejunior/safe-docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/@usejunior/safe-docx?label=npm%20downloads&color=2d7e5e" alt="npm downloads" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a class="trust-badge" href="https://github.com/usejunior/safe-docx/actions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/usejunior/safe-docx/ci.yml?label=CI&color=2d7e5e" alt="CI status" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a class="trust-badge" href="https://app.codecov.io/gh/UseJunior/safe-docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/UseJunior/safe-docx/main" alt="coverage" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="application/json" id="mcp-config">{
  "mcpServers": {
    "safe-docx": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@usejunior/safe-docx"]
    }
  }
}</script>
</section>

{# ── Value Props ─────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="grid reveal">
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>MIT-licensed. Read every line, fork it, vendor it. No black-box service calls, no usage metering.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Runs Locally</h2>
    <p>All edits happen in-process on your machine. Documents never leave your environment, even during AI-driven workflows.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Runs Anywhere JS Runs</h2>
    <p>Pure TypeScript. No native binaries, no .NET, no LibreOffice. Deploy in Cloudflare Workers, Vercel Edge, Lambda, or any V8 isolate.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Auditable by Design</h2>
    <p>Every operation is tested, traced, and published. Inspect the evidence before you ship.</p>
  </article>
</section>

{# ── Function Gallery ────────────────────────────── #}
<section id="functions" class="reveal">
  <h2 class="section-heading">22 tools across 7 categories</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    {% for cat in toolCatalog %}
    <article class="card">
      <h3>{{ cat.label }}</h3>
      <span class="tool-count">{{ cat.tools.length }} tool{{ "s" if cat.tools.length != 1 }}</span>
      <p>{{ cat.description }}</p>
      <ul class="tool-list">
        {% for tool in cat.tools %}
        <li><code>{{ tool }}</code></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ── Install ─────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section id="install" class="content reveal">
  <h2>Install</h2>
  <div class="install-cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Claude Desktop / MCP Client</h3>
      <p>Add this to your MCP client config:</p>
      <div class="install-pre-wrap">
        <pre><code>{
  "mcpServers": {
    "safe-docx": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@usejunior/safe-docx"]
    }
  }
}</code></pre>
        <button class="copy-btn" data-copy-target="mcp-config" aria-label="Copy MCP config">
          <span class="copy-label">Copy</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Gemini CLI Extension</h3>
      <p>Install as a Gemini CLI extension:</p>
      <div class="install-pre-wrap">
        <pre><code>gemini extensions install https://github.com/UseJunior/safe-docx</code></pre>
        <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="gemini extensions install https://github.com/UseJunior/safe-docx" aria-label="Copy Gemini CLI command">
          <span class="copy-label">Copy</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>npm</h3>
      <p>Install as a dependency:</p>
      <div class="install-pre-wrap">
        <pre><code>npm install @usejunior/safe-docx</code></pre>
        <button class="copy-btn" data-copy="npm install @usejunior/safe-docx" aria-label="Copy npm command">
          <span class="copy-label">Copy</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── FAQ ─────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section id="faq" class="content reveal">
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  {% for item in faq %}
  <details>
    <summary>{{ item.q }}</summary>
    <p>{{ item.a | safe }}</p>
  </details>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

{# ── Trust Callout ───────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="callout reveal">
  <h2>Built with trust evidence</h2>
  <p>992 automated tests · Per-package coverage · Published changelog · CI-regenerated on every commit</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="cta" href="trust/index.html">View Trust Evidence</a>
    <a class="cta cta-ghost" href="https://github.com/usejunior/safe-docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    <a class="cta cta-ghost" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@usejunior/safe-docx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">npm</a>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── FAQPage JSON-LD ─────────────────────────────── #}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {% for item in faq %}
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "{{ item.q }}",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "{{ item.a | striptags }}"
      }
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  ]
}
</script>
